      <p>Publish this dossier publicly. Create social media cards for each elected official. Engage Broward County media (Sun Sentinel, CBS Miami, WLRN).</p>

      <h3>Phase 4: Escalation (Days 14+)</h3>
      <p>Attend city commission meetings (public comment). Coordinate with Black candidates in the FL-20 race. Engage state-level Democratic Party officials.</p>

